{"tid":459538,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 辭職雙糧及Bonus問題","createTime":"2017-11-05T23:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T06:36:22.000Z","uid":28938,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"682bd9d02e3c08961da71d87b3a5cf12c38d16de","tid":459538,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:42:01.000Z","msg":"老婆做緊依間公司已經5年，因為想休息下，計劃明年1月1日辭職，兩個月通知期。<br />\n<br />\n雙糧同Bonus一般過年果時先會出。我上左勞工處網頁睇，雙糧就公司一定要出，因為上年截至12月31日老婆仲係為公司工作，但Bonus就公司可以唔出。<br />\n<br />\n\b請問各位我既理解是否正確？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d7f49f4f8a2b95aac8bb01cd90e011a127ef6b","tid":459538,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:45:10.000Z","msg":"一切睇合約"},{"pid":"b41750b7cd36942e3469ab4c358e22f21d0623bf","tid":459538,"uid":73092,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:46:00.000Z","msg":"最安全一定係過晒數袋咗錢先辭職"},{"pid":"0f4662c9cccff0f66475b401f1a7693c9671d3b4","tid":459538,"uid":1201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:13:39.000Z","msg":"唔並個幾個月啦<br />\n捱埋佢"},{"pid":"4859f177415d69318a7df6cab6998e417d51733f","tid":459538,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔並個幾個月啦<br />\n捱埋佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老婆應承左帶兩老去旅行，機票酒店都book哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ccf711421a89ace501a5ca5395d4735b4e1645","tid":459538,"uid":35666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:17:17.000Z","msg":"直接問HR"},{"pid":"d51332bc32fab8f8a93276fe58618fbc01587f36","tid":459538,"uid":155949,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最安全一定係過晒數袋咗錢先辭職</blockquote><br />\n正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce60e577db94a558bbbdc2d61c60c4c0d596e3c9","tid":459538,"uid":138427,"like":45,"dislike":0